title: Beginning Responsive Web Design with HTML5 and CSS3
description:
2014 | ISBN: 1430266945 | English | 328 pages | PDF | 13 MB

Beginning Responsive Web Design with HTML5 and CSS3 is your step-by-step guide to learning how to embrace responsive design for all devices.

You will learn how to develop your existing HTML, CSS, and JavaScript skills to make your sites work for the modern world.

Web sites and apps are now accessed on a wide range of devices with varied sizes and dimensions, so ensuring your users have the best experience now means thinking responsive
